{"tid":764390,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣死可以減低對身邊人嘅傷害","createTime":"2018-08-02T02:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T13:08:32.000Z","uid":8718,"like":8,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"69d01d5bdc93ed7255f2668c0d3857bd0d15ce1b","tid":764390,"uid":8718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"最近 同一個好好嘅朋友分左手<br />\n本身已經係無所不談 最後順理成章成為戀人<br />\n但因為自己唔成熟 對佢造成無可彌補嘅傷害<br />\n回想起自己曾經傷害過嘅人 <br />\n無一段關係都因為自己唔成熟 無自信 自卑<br />\n而傷害到對方<br />\n前排試過食藥自殺 最後救翻<br />\n但自殺嘅念頭無減少到 每一刻就係諗緊點死先唔會影響到身邊嘅人<br />\n我唔想再傷害人 <br />\n朋友搵我約我 我都推走哂<br />\n唔想再同任何人有任何接觸<br />\n無接觸 就唔會傷害<br />\n我想解脫"},{"pid":"d2cafceed34566dbe3afe26b88cead7c91568c7c","tid":764390,"uid":73531,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:53:23.000Z","msg":"我都想知 好想安靜咁消失"},{"pid":"2e79672b7f130b74da9a3319ed805382f94a792b","tid":764390,"uid":8718,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:54:55.000Z","msg":"我唔想再傷害人 離開咗就唔會傷害到人"},{"pid":"2d58841e6b57ead10d96dbbf88cea4656c04a4fb","tid":764390,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:55:02.000Z","msg":"No"},{"pid":"da7ec4353429c7ac0e59f418df35ddcf04814480","tid":764390,"uid":8718,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:56:40.000Z","msg":"再見啦各位 記住用心對人<br />\n唔好令自己後悔"},{"pid":"be2f0775aaa945edf5877f2bc67d3a32e8bf09b9","tid":764390,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"唔好死"},{"pid":"ccd16290085cf5ada79ef0173fb595c7a58305ab","tid":764390,"uid":140798,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"喂喂"},{"pid":"364e1c3298ccf9dadec3370f31c728fe72fa2e17","tid":764390,"uid":174949,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"唔好呀 你死咗仲傷害到身邊嘅人"},{"pid":"4e37504174af8c88192361732a3157f4a2d10ebd","tid":764390,"uid":8718,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"本身心臟有事 呢幾日無食藥<br />\n尋晚心跳得好大力 感受到自己接近死亡<br />\n想死同自殺嘅意念每日都纏繞住我"},{"pid":"3e1513ffe7105a92b9ddc43869c5c5d922e30e58","tid":764390,"uid":19762,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"白馬嘯西風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b53038511617eaa309785e210bb7f66b10bcb6","tid":764390,"uid":51561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:00:23.000Z","msg":"唔好死<br />\n<br />\n未唔會對身邊人有傷害囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n堅強d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162a846aa60f150f0784a43e16f697be15700688","tid":764390,"uid":8718,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:01:22.000Z","msg":"每次過馬路 都好想行前一步<br />\n但唔想累到人<br />\n每次行經商場邊位 都好想跳落去<br />\n但唔想嚇親人<br />\n有諗過係屋企燒炭<br />\n但又唔想累到屋企人<br />\n我已經唔想再行落去 所有錯都無辦法彌補"},{"pid":"ea0a4e52b519bc7e0a876986cdd6a0c4ec2a8634","tid":764390,"uid":51561,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:05:29.000Z","msg":"死=逃避<br />\n<br />\n你有手有腳有腦，係獨立個體<br />\n做咩因爲他人而了結自己生命？<br />\n事情都發生咗，路都要繼續行，你死咗過去嘅野唔會冇咗架喎<br />\n<br />\n有手有腳仲在世嘅，盡自己能力做好自己啦"},{"pid":"70dee85e5eda8b0159121bdd7daa614584f8a9fb","tid":764390,"uid":25179,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:06:04.000Z","msg":"如果我話俾你知我最近發生咩事一定嚇親你<br />\n唔係要比較邊個自殺念頭更大<br />\n只係你仲未有資格死"},{"pid":"dd4886c239c5c519f1f29c9a1cca4487ec6b4caa","tid":764390,"uid":8718,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"呢五年 我都無改變過<br />\n每一個人離開咗我生活都過得好好<br />\n我存在只係不斷拖人後蹆<br />\n唔想再累屋企人 朋友 好朋友"},{"pid":"dcd9b6f3c3a0c4a5cb805b9aa63df92749c62be6","tid":764390,"uid":126615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162a846aa60f150f0784a43e16f697be15700688","tid":764390,"uid":8718,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"reply